dct_description_sm: Map of the Cisalpine Republic. Relief shown by hachures. "Mit Kayserl. allergn. Freiheit." The Cisalpine Republic was created by Napoleon in 1797 by combining the Cispadane and Transpadane Republics. cf. Webster's new geographical dictionary. Historic Maps copy imperfect: upper-left hand corner torn.
